#. type: =head1
#: lib/Locale/Po4a/AsciiDoc.pm:6 lib/Locale/Po4a/BibTeX.pm:7
#: lib/Locale/Po4a/Man.pm:34 lib/Locale/Po4a/Po.pm:13 lib/Locale/Po4a/Sgml.pm:7
